export const skillsImage = (skill) => {
    const skillID = skill.toLowerCase();
    switch (skillID) {
   
        case 'Ubuntu':
            return ubuntu;
        case 'html':
            return html;
        case 'photoshop':
            return photoshop;
       
        case 'css':
            return css;
       
        case 'javascript':
            return javascript;
        case 'next js':
            return nextJS;
        
        case 'react':
            return react;
      
        case 'typescript':
            return typescript;
       
        case 'bootstrap':
            return bootstrap;
        
        case 'mysql':
            return mysql;
       
        case 'tailwind':
            return tailwind;
       
        case 'java':
            return java;
        
        case 'php':
            return php;
        case 'python':
            return python;
        
        case 'firebase':
            return firebase;
        
        case 'git':
            return git;
       
        case 'microsoft office':
            return microsoftoffice;
       
        case 'canva':
            return canva;
        default:
            break;
    }
}
